1. *Nik* nema nikakvih obaveza. (He has no obligations.)
2. Ona nikad neće zaboraviti njegovo ime. (She will never forget his name.)
3. On nikada nije bio tako usamljen. (He had never been so lonely.)
4. *Nik* nije imao šta da izgubi. (He had nothing to lose.)
5. Nikada nisam razmišljao o tome. (I never thought about it.)
6. *Nik* nije mogao da vidi svoje dete. (He couldn't see his child.)
7. Nisam mogla da verujem u to. (I couldn't believe it.)
8. *Nik* nije mogao da se odluči. (He couldn't decide.)